<subSubSection id="C34065156322FFD8FF12FB39FB6AF9C3" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BE5369E6322FFD8FF12FB39FE25FAE3" blockId="19.[151,1437,1231,1581]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FF12FB39FE8AFB07" bold="true" box="[151,269,1231,1257]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">Remarks:</emphasis>
The original collector’s label is still attached (
<figureCitation id="13612A1B6322FFD8FCADFB39FC1CFB04" box="[808,923,1231,1258]" captionStart="FIGURE 6" captionStartId="16.[151,250,787,811]" captionTargetBox="[155,1435,186,761]" captionTargetId="figure-24@16.[149,1437,181,763]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURE 6. Labels of type specimens in the NHMO Bird Collection described by T. Salvadori. a) Ptilotis erythropleura NHMO-BI-86778 (collector’s label); b) Melanocharis chloroptera NHMO-BI-61863 (NHMO label); c) Zosterops novae guineae NHMO-BI-86649 (NHMO label); d) Dicaeum misoriense NHMO-BI-61856 (collector’s label)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6626777" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6626777/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">Figure 6d</figureCitation>
), showing that this is specimen 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FA8AFB39FA90FB06" box="[1295,1303,1231,1256]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">i</emphasis>
of the 
<typeStatus id="54E1883C6322FFD8FAE9FB39FA1BFB07" box="[1388,1436,1231,1257]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">type</typeStatus>
series (
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB4B6F6322FFD8FF63FB05FE11FAE3" author="Salvadori, T." box="[230,406,1267,1293]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" refId="ref16401" refString="Salvadori, T. (1881) Ornitologia della Papuasia e delle Molucche. Vol. 2. Stamperia Reale della ditta G. B. Paravia E Comp., Torino, 705 pp." type="book" year="1881">Salvadori 1881</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE5369E6322FFD8FF42FAE1FB6AF9C3" blockId="19.[151,1437,1231,1581]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">
Of the 
<specimenCount id="9D5CFD176322FFD8FE96FAE1FE2DFADF" box="[275,426,1303,1329]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" type="generic">10 specimens</specimenCount>
mentioned in the original description (
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB4B6F6322FFD8FCDDFAE1FB94FADC" author="Salvadori, T." box="[856,1043,1303,1330]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" pagination="896 - 976" refId="ref16237" refString="Salvadori, T. (1876 a) Descrizione di cinquantotto nuove specie di uccelli, ed osservazioni intorno ad altre poco note, della Nuova Guinea e di altre Isole Papuane, raccolte dal D. r Odoardo Beccari e dai cacciatori del Sig. A. A. Bruijn. Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova, 7, 896 - 976. [1875]" type="journal article" year="1876">Salvadori 1876a</bibRefCitation>
), 
<specimenCount id="9D5CFD176322FFD8FBA0FAE1FB2CFADF" box="[1061,1195,1303,1329]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" type="generic" typeStatus="syntype">one syntype</specimenCount>
(not two, as stated by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB4B6F6322FFD8FF12FACDFEC0FABB" author="LeCroy, M." box="[151,327,1339,1365]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" pagination="1 - 169" refId="ref15000" refString="LeCroy, M. (2010) Type specimens of birds in the American Museum of Natural History. Part 8. Passeriformes: Pachycephalidae, Aegithalidae, Remizidae, Paridae, Sittidae, Neosittidae, Certhiidae, Rhabdornithidae, Climacteridae, Dicaeidae, Pardalotidae, and Nectariniidae. Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History, 333, 1 - 169. https: // doi. org / 10.1206 / 682.1" type="journal article" year="2010">LeCroy (2010))</bibRefCitation>
is still in MSNG in Genoa (C.E. 11278; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB4B6F6322FFD8FC81FACDFC64FABB" author="Arbocco, G. &amp; Capocaccia, L. &amp; Violani, C." box="[772,995,1339,1365]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" pagination="184 - 265" refId="ref13577" refString="Arbocco, G., Capocaccia, L. &amp; Violani, C. (1979) Catalogo dei tipi di uccelli del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova. Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova, 82, 184 - 265." type="journal article" year="1979">
Arbocco 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FCEFFACDFC25FABB" box="[874,930,1339,1365]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">et al.</emphasis>
1979
</bibRefCitation>
), corresponding to specimen 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FAA2FACDFAB4FABA" box="[1319,1331,1339,1364]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">c</emphasis>
in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB4B6F6322FFD8FAD0FACDFE92FA97" author="Salvadori, T." pageId="19" pageNumber="470" refId="ref16401" refString="Salvadori, T. (1881) Ornitologia della Papuasia e delle Molucche. Vol. 2. Stamperia Reale della ditta G. B. Paravia E Comp., Torino, 705 pp." type="book" year="1881">Salvadori (1881)</bibRefCitation>
(Enrico Borgo, pers. comm.). Two 
<typeStatus id="54E1883C6322FFD8FD18FAA9FD78FA97" box="[669,767,1375,1401]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">syntypes</typeStatus>
are in MRSN; MZUT Av3943 and MZUT Av3944 (
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB4B6F6322FFD8FABAFAA9FE97FA73" author="Aimassi, G. &amp; Pulcher, C. &amp; Ghiraldi, L." pageId="19" pageNumber="470" pagination="65 - 154" refId="ref13467" refString="Aimassi, G., Pulcher, C. &amp; Ghiraldi, L. (2020) Type specimens of birds in the Museo Regionale di Scienze Naturali (Torino, Italy). Journal of the National Museum (Prague), Natural History Series, 189, 65 - 154. https: // doi. org / 10.37520 / jnmpnhs. 2020.007" type="journal article" year="2020">
Aimassi 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FF12FA75FF49FA73" box="[151,206,1411,1437]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">et al.</emphasis>
2020
</bibRefCitation>
), corresponding to specimens 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FDDBFA75FDEBFA72" box="[606,620,1411,1436]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">a</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FD1AFA75FD20FA72" box="[671,679,1411,1436]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">j</emphasis>
, respectively. The date on the original label of the latter (specimen 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FA0EFA75FA14FA72" box="[1419,1427,1411,1436]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">j</emphasis>
) is 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FF34FA51FE8DFA2F" box="[177,266,1447,1473]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">‘8.5.75’</emphasis>
(Giorgio Aimassi and Luca Ghiraldi, pers. comm.) while 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB4B6F6322FFD8FC14FA51FBCAFA2F" author="Salvadori, T." box="[913,1101,1447,1473]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" refId="ref16401" refString="Salvadori, T. (1881) Ornitologia della Papuasia e delle Molucche. Vol. 2. Stamperia Reale della ditta G. B. Paravia E Comp., Torino, 705 pp." type="book" year="1881">Salvadori (1881)</bibRefCitation>
reported it as 
<date id="FFE4105E6322FFD8FB68FA51FAF2FA2F" box="[1261,1397,1446,1473]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" value="1875-05-03">3 May 1875</date>
(
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FA00FA51FEB2FA0B" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">
‘ 
<date id="FFE4105E6322FFD8FA0FFA51FEB6FA0B" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" value="1875-05-03">3 Maggio 1875</date>
’
</emphasis>
); this may, however, be just a misreading of either the 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FC11FA3DFC32FA0B" box="[916,949,1483,1509]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">‘3’</emphasis>
as 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FC5DFA3DFC7EFA0B" box="[984,1017,1483,1509]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">‘8’</emphasis>
, or 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FBA1FA3DFB13FA0A" box="[1060,1172,1483,1508]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">vice versa</emphasis>
. Three more specimens (698077–698079, corresponding to specimens 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FD21FA19FD37F9E6" box="[676,688,1519,1544]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">e</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FD3BFA19FD4BF9E6" box="[702,716,1519,1544]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">g</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis id="B92EEA8C6322FFD8FC87FA19FC97F9E7" box="[770,784,1519,1545]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="470">d</emphasis>
, respectively, of 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB4B6F6322FFD8FC55FA19FB11F9E7" author="Salvadori, T." box="[976,1174,1519,1545]" pageId="19" pageNumber="470" refId="ref16401" refString="Salvadori, T. (1881) Ornitologia della Papuasia e delle Molucche. Vol. 2. Stamperia Reale della ditta G. B. Paravia E Comp., Torino, 705 pp." type="book" year="1881">Salvadori (1881))</bibRefCitation>
are in AMNH (
<bibRefCitation id="EFCB4B6F6322FFD8FAC0FA19FF54F9C3" author="LeCroy, M." pageId="19" pageNumber="470" pagination="1 - 169" refId="ref15000" refString="LeCroy, M. (2010) Type specimens of birds in the American Museum of Natural History. Part 8. Passeriformes: Pachycephalidae, Aegithalidae, Remizidae, Paridae, Sittidae, Neosittidae, Certhiidae, Rhabdornithidae, Climacteridae, Dicaeidae, Pardalotidae, and Nectariniidae. Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History, 333, 1 - 169. https: // doi. org / 10.1206 / 682.1" type="journal article" year="2010">LeCroy 2010</bibRefCitation>
), having arrived there with the Rothschild collection from Tring (
